dct_title_s: Essex County, New Jersey color map 1889
dct_description_sm: County street map color coded by township and indicating hills, mountains and undeveloped areas. Map compiled expressly for F. N. Moffet by Scarlett and Scarlett, Surveyors and Engineers, 800 Broad St., Newark, N.J. Real Estate agent Frank B. Wilson has lengthy advertisement printed below map title.
